But I&#39;d rather use it for module-info.java only.

## SuppressionFilter


This filter is more specific, as it will only suppress a specific check.

```xml
  &lt;module name=&quot;SuppressionSingleFilter&quot;&gt;
    &lt;property name=&quot;checks&quot; value=&quot;MagicNumber&quot; /&gt;
